########################################
## CONFIGURING BUILD AGENTS ON UBUNTU ##
########################################



## ON AGENT NODE

1. INSTALL JAVA
$sudo apt update
$sudo apt install openjdk-11-jdk -y

2. Create a user and set password
$sudo useradd bob -m --shell /bin/bash --home-dir /home/bob
$sudo passwd bob



## ON JENKINS

1. Install "SSH Build Agents" Jenkins plugin.
2. Make username/password credentials
3. Create a Permanent Agent type agent node
